reviewText: this is the perfect action pack the only way it could be better is with a family movie like game plan or tooth fairy
Great movies love the rock in any movie he is in . Wish that he would be in more movies
This three pack of Dwayne Johnson is great. It is fantastic to see him in his earlier work. Many thanks.

Good for Rock fans. Scorpion King is his best of these 3. Surprising to me that his acting isn't better though. He was great at live entertainment and only so-so as an actor. Walking Tall is his best film and is unfortunately not included in this 3 pack.
Well worth the money. Lots of good stuff here.
It's the rock what else is there to say he can do no wrong lol
